    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Aid</strong> (Level 2 Abjuration)</p><p>Your spell bolsters your allies with toughness and resolve. Choose up to three creatures within range. Each target's hit point maximum and current hit points increase by 5 for the duration.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, a target's hit points increase by an additional 5 for each slot level above 2nd.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (A tiny strip of white cloth.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> 30 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> 8 hours</p><p><em>Classes: Cleric, Paladin</em></p>",
